nodes.text: deVores was a general in the Galactic Empire. In 5 ABY, Grand Admiral Rae Sloane was supposed to have a meeting involving troop movements with deVores, yet instead she lied and said that she had a meeting with Ferric Obdur in propaganda, but to Obdur Sloane stated that she had a meeting with Vice Admiral Gaelan, yet in fact she had none of these.
